# Theme & Design

## Single source of truth
`lib/src/core/theme/app_theme.dart` — the `MaterialTheme` class generated from Material Theme Builder
(seed `#1B5E20`, deep green). This file contains all six schemes: light, dark, lightMediumContrast,
lightHighContrast, darkMediumContrast, darkHighContrast.

**Never** pass inline `ThemeData`, `ColorScheme`, or `TextStyle` in widgets.
Always read from `Theme.of(context).colorScheme` and `Theme.of(context).textTheme`.

## MaterialApp.router setup in app.dart
```dart
MaterialApp.router(
  theme: MaterialTheme(Theme.of(context).textTheme).light(),
  darkTheme: MaterialTheme(Theme.of(context).textTheme).dark(),
  themeMode: ThemeMode.system,
  routerConfig: appRouter,
)
```

## Deadline urgency colour convention
Map `closes_at` proximity to M3 semantic colours — use these, nowhere else:
| State                       | Background                       | Foreground                      |
|-----------------------------|----------------------------------|---------------------------------|
| Closing ≤ 3 days            | `colorScheme.errorContainer`     | `colorScheme.onErrorContainer`  |
| Closing 4–7 days            | `colorScheme.tertiaryContainer`  | `colorScheme.onTertiaryContainer` |
| Open > 7 days               | `colorScheme.primaryContainer`   | `colorScheme.onPrimaryContainer`|
| Upcoming (not yet open)     | `colorScheme.secondaryContainer` | `colorScheme.onSecondaryContainer` |
| Closed                      | `colorScheme.surfaceContainerHighest` | `colorScheme.outline`      |

Helper — put this in `lib/src/core/utils/deadline_utils.dart`, not in widgets:
```dart
DeadlineState classifyDeadline(DateTime? closesAt) { ... }
```

## Component choices (use these, not custom alternatives)
- **Programme list cards**: `Card` — elevation 0, `color: colorScheme.surfaceContainerLow`, `borderRadius: 12`
- **Filter chips**: `FilterChip` — `side: BorderSide.none`, `selectedColor: colorScheme.primaryContainer`
- **Bottom navigation**: `NavigationBar` (M3). NOT the legacy `BottomNavigationBar`.
- **Filter sheet**: `showModalBottomSheet` with `isScrollControlled: true`, `useSafeArea: true`
- **Primary CTA ("Apply / Visit")**: `FilledButton`
- **Secondary actions**: `OutlinedButton`
- **Countdown badge**: M3 `Badge` widget on card trailing corner
- **Status pill**: `Chip` — colours from urgency table above
- **Search**: `SearchBar` (M3) at top of Browse screen
- **Programme detail hero**: `SliverAppBar` with `pinned: true`, `expandedHeight: 180`

## Typography — M3 scale, no custom fonts at MVP
| Use case                  | Style           |
|---------------------------|-----------------|
| Programme name (card)     | `titleMedium`   |
| Deadline countdown        | `labelLarge`    |
| Programme description     | `bodyMedium`    |
| Stipend amount            | `titleSmall`    |
| Section labels            | `labelMedium`   |
| Detail screen body        | `bodyLarge`     |
